OL,7,GYou get what you pay for. It's an old
OL,8,Gcliche but it applies to the BBC's
OL,9,Gfinancial situation.
OL,11,FThe announcement concerning the future
OL,12,Fof Newsnight highlights the BBC's
OL,13,Ffinancial problems.
OL,15,FI have discussed Newsnight's declining
OL,16,Faudience before and whether it had a
OL,17,Ffuture in its traditional form.
