OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FOther major BBC news programmes are
OL,8,Fprincipally reliant on reporters and
OL,9,Fcorrespondents who work across TV,
OL,10,Fradio and online.
OL,12,FThey might be commissioned to do
OL,13,Fstories across all three platforms or
OL,14,Fon "reactive" stories they will have
OL,15,Fparticular outlets to service.
OL,17,FIt is vitally important that a
OL,18,Fmeaningful platform is found for the
OL,19,Fkind of in-depth journalism which
OL,20,FNewsnight at its best offers.
