OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FIt is also vitally important to retain
OL,8,Fthe skills of the individuals. Any
OL,9,Fcompulsory redundancies would be
OL,10,Ffiercely opposed by the NUJ and would
OL,11,Fbe likely to lead to industrial action.
OL,13,FBut sadly allowing one programme alone
OL,14,Fsuch a large, dedicated team (with
OL,15,Fwork which rarely featured on other
OL,16,Flinear outlets despite its quality) is
OL,17,Fa luxury the BBC cannot afford just
OL,18,Fnow with the very real squeeze on its
OL,19,Fincome.
OL,21,FAnyone who feels otherwise needs to
OL,22,Fsay where the money would come from.
