OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FThe BBC needs more money if it is to
OL,8,Fsurvive in its current form.
OL,10,FThere needs to be a proper public
OL,11,Fdebate ahead of the general election.
OL,13,FAre there realistic alternatives to
OL,14,Fthe licence fee as a form of direct
OL,15,Fpublic funding? The suggestion of a
OL,16,F"household charge" added to council
OL,17,Ftax bills at a level which varies
OL,18,Faccording to council tax bands is
OL,19,Fcertainly interesting.
