OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FOr is a flat rate charge still the
OL,8,Fleast worst option? And if so what
OL,9,Fshould the charge be?
OL,11,FThere would seem to be a high chance
OL,12,Fat present of a Labour government
OL,13,Fafter the next election. What will be
OL,14,Fin their manifesto?
OL,16,FWill they keep the licence fee? Commit
OL,17,Fto a one-off restorative rise? Then
OL,18,Fannual rises in line with inflation?
