OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FOr would this simply give political
OL,8,Fopponents an opportunity to say a
OL,9,FLabour government would cost voters
OL,10,Fmoney?
OL,12,FIt's not an easy time for all of us
OL,13,Fwho care about public service
OL,14,Fbroadcasting.
OL,16,FIt must be efficiently run and provide
OL,17,Fbest value for money.
OL,19,FBut serious journalism must always be
OL,20,Fat its heart, even if we can discuss
OL,21,Fhow it is best provided.
